<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''先天性心臟病'''（{{lang|en|Congenital heart defect, CHD}}）是指在嬰兒[[出生|出生]]時就已有的[[心臟|心臟]]問題<ref name=NIH2011>{{cite web|title=What Are Congenital Heart Defects?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd|website=National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute|accessdate=10 August 2015|date=July 1, 2011|archive-date=2015-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813182642/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。徵象和症状隨心臟問題的種類而不同<ref name=WHO2011/>。症状可能很輕微，也可能危及生命<ref name=NIH2011/>。若有症狀，可能會包括呼吸急促、[[發紺|發紺]]、體重增加緩慢、以及容易疲倦<ref name=NIH2011Sym/>。一般不會有胸痛的症狀<ref name=NIH2011Sym>{{cite web|title=What Are the Signs and Symptoms of Congenital Heart Defects?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/signs|website=National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute|accessdate=10 August 2015|date=July 1, 2011|archive-date=2015-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727210816/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/signs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大部份的先天性心臟病不會和其他疾病一起出現<ref name=WHO2011>{{cite book|author1=Shanthi Mendis|author2=Pekka Puska|author3=Bo Norrving|author4=World Health Organization|title=Global Atlas on Cardiovascular Disease Prevention and Control|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2011/9789241564373_eng.pdf?ua=1|year=2011|publisher=World Health Organization in collaboration with the World Heart Federation and the World Stroke Organization|pages=3, 60|isbn=978-92-4-156437-3|access-date=2016-01-20|archive-date=2014-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817123106/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2011/9789241564373_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。心臟缺陷可能會造成其他併發症，包括[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]]<ref name=NIH2011Sym/>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis-->
先天性心臟病的成因大多未知<ref>{{cite web|title=What Causes Congenital Heart Defects?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/causes|website=National,Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute|accessdate=10 August 2015|date=July 1, 2011|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708122049/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/causes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。部分的病例歸因於在[[懷孕|懷孕]]時期的感染（如[[德國麻疹|德國麻疹]]）、使用特定藥物或有毒物質（如[[酒精|酒精]]或[[菸|菸]]），而父母親也和此疾病有關連，如母親的營養不良或[[肥胖|肥胖]]<ref name=WHO2011/><ref name=Dean2014>{{cite journal|last1=Dean|first1=SV|last2=Lassi|first2=ZS|last3=Imam|first3=AM|last4=Bhutta|first4=ZA|title=Preconception care: nutritional risks and interventions.|journal=Reproductive health|date=26 September 2014|volume=11 Suppl 3|pages=S3|pmid=25415364|doi=10.1186/1742-4755-11-s3-s3}}</ref>。父母親其中一方有先天性心臟病也是危險因子<ref name=Mil2011/>。某些基因的狀況也會和此心臟疾病有關，如[[唐氏症|唐氏症]]、[[透納氏症|透納氏症]]，和[[馬凡氏症候群|馬凡氏症候群]]<ref name=WHO2011/>。先天性心臟病可以分成兩類：{{le|發紺性心臟病|Cyanotic heart defect}}和{{le|非發紺性心臟病|Acyanotic heart defect}}，是依兒童是否會[[發紺|發紺]]來分。<ref name=NIH2011/>心臟病的發病位置可以包含心臟的內壁、心臟瓣膜，或是流入心臟或流出心臟的大血管<ref name=NIH2011/>。
<!-- Prevention and treatment -->

先天性心臟病可以透過接種[[德國麻疹|德國麻疹]]疫苗、含有[[碘|碘]]的鹽，及添加了[[葉酸|葉酸]]的某些食物製品，來達到部分的預防功效<ref name=NIH2011/>。某些情況下它是不需要被治療的
<ref name=NIH2011/>，其他則可以透過[[心導管手術|心導管手術]]或[[心臟外科手術|心臟外科手術]]完成有效的治療<ref name=NIH2011Tx/>。有時則需要[[心臟移植|心臟移植]]<ref name=NIH2011Tx>{{cite web|title=How Are Congenital Heart Defects Treated?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/treatment|website=National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute|accessdate=10 August 2015|date=July 1, 2011|archive-date=2015-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727210805/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/treatment|dead-url=no}}</ref>。只要有適當的治療，即便病情再複雜，治療成果通常良好<ref name=NIH2011/>。

<!-- Epidemiology and prognosis -->
心臟疾病是最常見的[[先天缺陷|先天缺陷]]<ref name=WHO2011/><ref name=GBD2015/>。在2013年，全球有3430萬人罹患此疾病<ref name=GBD2015>{{cite journal|last1=Global Burden of Disease Study 2013|first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national incidence, prevalence, and years lived with disability for 301 acute and chronic diseases and injuries in 188 countries, 1990–2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013|journal=Lancet (London, England)|date=7 June 2015|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(15)60692-4|pmid=26063472}}</ref>。根據診查狀況，先天性心臟病每千名活產新生兒大約可影響4至75人<ref name=WHO2011/><ref name=Mil2011>{{cite book|last1=Milunsky|first1=Aubrey|title=Genetic Disorders and the Fetus: Diagnosis, Prevention and Treatment|date=2011|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9781444358216|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=yY-gIvbnRDUC&pg=PT28|chapter=1|access-date=2016-01-20|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305051354/https://books.google.ca/books?id=yY-gIvbnRDUC&pg=PT28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而大約每千名活產新生兒內有6至19人可能有輕微至嚴重的病情<ref name=Mil2011/>。先天性心臟病是最主要先天疾病相關的死因<ref name=WHO2011/>。在2013年，先天性心臟病造成了323,000人的死亡，這個數字較1990年的366,000人死亡來的低<ref name=GDB2013>{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2013 Mortality and Causes of Death|first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national age-sex specific all-cause and cause-specific mortality for 240 causes of death, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013.|journal=Lancet|date=17 December 2014|pmid=25530442|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(14)61682-2|volume=385|pages=117–71|pmc=4340604}}</ref>。

